/* ==UserStyle==
@name           J×Y Skin affecting CSS Fixes Project for Dueling Nexus - 2019-08-31, 9:51:03 p.m.
@namespace      github.com/openstyles/stylus
@version        0.3.0
@description   Jaden and Yubel v3.0
